FAQ'S SECTION

Some Common FAQ's

Get answers to your questions and learn about our platform

Is Nexura free for creators?

Yes. Creators can join, build a profile, and get discovered for free. We only charge brands a commission when a partnership is successful.

How do brands find the right creators?

Brands use filters, campaign goals, and our analytics-driven dashboard to find creators that match their audience. They can also book demos before launching a campaign.

How is Nexura better than traditional influencer agencies?

Traditional influencer marketing often revolves around a handful of creators managed by exclusive agents, limiting your reach and options. Nexura breaks that model by offering access to a wide network of independent creators across different niches and audience sizes — giving your brand more reach, better targeting, and flexible pricing.

Can brands try Nexura before paying?

Yes. Brands can explore profiles, shortlist creators, and even request a demo session before committing to a campaign or plan.

How is this better than reaching out to creators manually?

With Nexura, brands skip DMs and guesswork. They get verified creators, smart filters, data-backed matches, and structured campaigns — all in one place.
